== O|B|F Codefests ==

Since 2010, people from the O|B|F project communities have organized or co-organized short 2-3 day events focused on collaborative coding, documentation, and better interoperation between O|B|F and other bioinformatics open-source projects.

* [[Codefest 2013]]: July 17-18, 2013, in Berlin, Germany.
* [[EU Codefest 2012]]: July 19-20, 2012, in Lodi, Italy.
* [[Codefest 2012]]: July 11-12, 2012, at Loyola Marymount University, Los Angeles, CA, USA.
* [[Codefest 2011]]: July 13-14, 2011, in Vienna, Austria.
* [[Codefest 2010]]: July 7-8, 2010, in Boston, MA, USA.

